GTG for now.

::Striker::

Striker's eyes widen as the Ark comes in view. He looks over the new crater, 
frowning. He lands near it, setting Spears down.

"If the Predacons keep attacking here, they'll whipe everyone from history," 
he mutters, looking at the damage.
